::DarkMouse::

She lookes up at Quickstrike. "It healed right away."
She looks back at her hand. "It..I cut it...and now it's all healed 
up...What happened? It should still be cut and oozing, but...but it's 
not." her hand was trembling and the rest of her was shaking.
"Quickstrike, I'm scared."
